message.content: The most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with natural language processing and question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper involves machine learning techniques, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses low-dimensional embeddings, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the paper deals with retrieving answers from a knowledge base, and "cs.DB" (Databases) as the paper involves structured representations of answers.
